item.title: [HIVE-18573] Use proper Calcite operator instead of UDFs
item.description: Currently, Hive is mostly using user-defined black box sql operators during Query planning. It will be more beneficial to use proper calcite operators, this is to prepare the ground for pushing complex expressions to Druid-calcite adapter.
item.summary: Use proper Calcite operator instead of UDFs
